# Base URL for the Eiswein API.
# - Dev (default): leave empty. Fetch uses relative /api/* paths and Vite's
#   dev-server proxy (see vite.config.ts) forwards them to the backend.
#   Setting this to http://localhost:8000 bypasses the proxy and hits the
#   backend cross-origin — CORS blocks that. Don't do it.
# - Prod: leave empty. FastAPI serves the built SPA + API on the same origin.
# - Only set a value when the frontend is deployed to a different host than
#   the backend (e.g., previewing against a remote staging API).
VITE_API_URL=
